---

## ⚙️ Features

| Feature | Detail |
|---|---|
| **Indices** | Sensex, Nifty 50, India VIX |
| **Sectors** | 12 NSE sector indices (parallel fetch) |
| **Alerts** | Drop ≥1% from prev close |
| **VIX Alert** | If VIX spikes ≥15% or reaches ≥25 |
| **RSI Alert** | Nifty RSI ≥75 (overbought) or ≤25 (oversold) |
| **Sector Alert** | Any sector drops ≥2% |
| **Rotation Signal** | Identifies leading sector + market narrative |
| **Breadth** | How many sectors up vs down |
| **CSV** | Auto-committed with sector columns |

---

## 🌡️ India VIX Zones

| Range | Zone | Action |
|---|---|---|
| < 13 | 🟢 ULTRA LOW | Watch for complacency reversal |
| 13–15 | 🟢 LOW | Bullish bias — ride the trend |
| 15–18 | 🟡 MODERATE | Normal — mild caution |
| 18–20 | 🟠 ELEVATED | Reduce leveraged bets |
| 20–25 | 🔴 HIGH | Defensive positioning |
| 25–30 | 🔴 VERY HIGH | Panic — reduce exposure |
| > 30 | ⛔ EXTREME | Crisis — max caution |

